data.description: Home has been remodeled with new bathroom fixtures, new appliances, large master bedroom and bath.  Deck off of master bedroom, front porch with mature shade trees.  Home is at the end of a quiet street on almost half acre lot.  380 sq ft shed in back.  Location is 15 miles south of I-10, 9 minutes to Elberta school and 11 minutes to Summerdale.
